                     <xar:mlstring> Click on Version History tab at the bottom to get the latest release information.</xar:mlstring>
                 </li>
                 <li><xar:mlstring>Related tutorials and documentation on xarTinyMCE found at </xar:mlstring> <a href="http://www.xaraya.com/index.php/keywords/xartinymce/" title="#xarML('Related documentation on XarTinyMCE')#"><xar:mlstring>Xaraya Documentation</xar:mlstring></a>
                 </li>
             </ul>
